ul.li:

identifies the evaluation of conditions that impact an activity or its 
execution. the module records the parameter values evaluated and the 
logicalresult of the evaluation;


captures the specification of a property 
of an activity, the representation of a property of an activity, 
or the use of an independent property in the definition of an activity;


provides for the assignment of a property to product data, use of an 
independent property in the definition of an item and the association 
of a representation with a property;
